      "episodeResult": "Recall questions avoid brittle substring heuristics.",
      "episodeLesson": "Prefer model-based no-memory verification over hard-coded substring matching.",
      "firstText": "Lesson: prefer model-based no-memory verification over hard-coded substring matching.",
